Baiklah.

117
00:03:41,240 --> 00:03:42,600
Ada pelayanan seperti ini?

118
00:03:42,600 --> 00:03:43,199
Benar begitu.

119
00:03:44,080 --> 00:03:44,679
Tambahkan kekuatanmu.

120
00:03:44,679 --> 00:03:45,160
Oke.

121
00:03:45,160 --> 00:03:46,639
Pria kekar memijat.

122
00:03:47,080 --> 00:03:48,080
Lumayan enak.

123
00:03:48,479 --> 00:03:49,520
Kalau begitu, aku lanjut menuang air.

124
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:50,399
Oke, tidak masalah.

125
00:03:50,399 --> 00:03:51,679
Terima kasih.

126
00:03:51,679 --> 00:03:53,839
Ayo, makan.

127
