Semuanya, makanlah.

128
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:56,639
Semuanya, ayo kembali dan makan.

129
00:03:56,639 --> 00:03:57,520
Baik, segera.

130
00:03:58,440 --> 00:04:00,279
Aku duduk di sini, ya.

131
00:04:00,279 --> 00:04:01,759
Terima kasih atas kerja kerasnya.

132
00:04:01,759 --> 00:04:02,559
Aku duduk di sini.

133
00:04:04,600 --> 00:04:04,919
Oke.

134
00:04:05,960 --> 00:04:06,679
Tidak apa-apa, kita bisa...

135
00:04:09,980 --> 00:04:12,260
