Namun, kau punya gigi taring.

562
00:17:25,199 --> 00:17:26,319
Aku tidak tersenyum.

563
00:17:26,319 --> 00:17:27,199
Kau tersenyum.

564
00:17:27,880 --> 00:17:28,880
Gawat.

565
00:17:30,439 --> 00:17:33,160
Penuh percaya diri.

566
00:17:33,160 --> 00:17:34,640
Aku punya gigi taring waktu kecil.

567
00:17:39,040 --> 00:17:40,160
Kau salah pilih.

568
