658
00:20:37,640 --> 00:20:41,479
Setiap tim penduduk pulau dipersilakan
menuju Arena Bertahan Hidup.

659
00:20:41,479 --> 00:20:43,119
Misi pasangan terakhir

660
00:20:43,119 --> 00:20:45,880
