663
00:20:52,959 --> 00:20:54,359
Entahlah.

664
00:20:54,359 --> 00:20:56,000
Lagi-lagi arena pertarungan.

665
00:20:56,000 --> 00:20:57,599
Benar. Hari ini, harus lebih rendah hati.

666
00:20:57,599 --> 00:20:58,880
Iya, santai saja.

667
00:20:59,020 --> 00:21:00,280
