tapi jangan terlalu agresif.

673
00:21:12,520 --> 00:21:14,280
Kita sudah cukup sampai di sini.

674
00:21:14,280 --> 00:21:15,319
Hari ini, kita mengalah saja.

675
00:21:15,319 --> 00:21:16,760
Oke.

676
00:21:16,760 --> 00:21:18,160
