712
00:22:34,839 --> 00:22:36,160
Hati-hati, yang penting jangan terluka.

713
00:22:36,160 --> 00:22:37,280
Kita bisa.

714
00:22:37,460 --> 00:22:38,479
(Sangat percaya diri)

715
00:22:38,479 --> 00:22:40,040
Aku pasti akan berusaha.

716
00:22:40,040 --> 00:22:41,119
Bagaimanapun juga,

717
00:22:41,119 --> 00:22:43,920
